quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,57,"When the example of the son of Mary was given, your people laughed and jeered"
  43,58,"and they said, “Are Our gods better or he?” They only mentioned him to you for the sake of argument. They are indeed a contentious people"
  43,59,He was only a slave whom We favored and made him an example for the Children of Israel
  43,60,"If We willed, We could [destroy you and] replace you with angels, succeeding one another on earth"
  43,61,"And he [Jesus] will be a sign of the Hour; so do not have doubt about it and follow me. This is a straight path"
  43,62,"Do not let Satan turn you away [from the straight path], for he is your sworn enemy"
  43,63,"When Jesus came with clear signs, he said, “I have come to you with wisdom, and to clarify to you some of that concerning which you differ; so fear Allah and obey me"
  43,64,"Indeed, Allah is my Lord and your Lord; so worship Him. This is a straight path.”"
  43,65,"But the factions differed among themselves [about Jesus]; so woe to the wrongdoers from the punishment of a painful Day"
  43,66,Are they waiting except for the Hour to come upon them by surprise when they least expect it
  43,67,"On that Day, close friends will become enemies to one another, except the righteous"